B. Monthly Release Cycle — stages & timings
Q: List the main stages of a monthly release.
A: Release Tagging → Baseline Merging → Package Preparation for Baseline → Baseline Testing → Release Notes → Package Preparation (for release) → Release/Regression Testing → Live Server Rollouts. 
