Q: Summarize the Day N → Day N+1 flow for a daily release.
A: Consolidate issues (Day N) → Dev fixes (Day N) → QA tests → Developer creates Deployment Task → approvals before cutoff → deploy to release server at 1:00 PM Day N+1 → QA verifies (1:00–2:00 PM) → DevOps deploys to production (2:00–3:00 PM) → scrum QA verifies in client environment post-deploy. 
